  "method": [
    "Preheat the oven to 400°F.",
    "Add all the chickpea ball ingredients to a food processor. Pulse until the chickpeas are broken down and the ingredients are mixed. Form mixture into twenty-four bean balls and place them on a baking sheet. Bake for 25 minutes.",
